## 8. Ordering constraints
1. Atomic lockstep: ops ⇄ pack codec ⇄ round-trip table; Fold dispatch ⇄ prefixFolder; trail/titleOf/checkpoint cases in the same commit as anything minting runbook refs.
2. Build order: model (types → position → ops → pack → snapshot) → internal/refs → internal/fold (foldRunbook + dispatch + 12 edits + history.go) → internal/store (write → resolve → read → dedupe → cache) → internal/trail.
3. Out of core scope but same-release gates: viz summaryOf/classify, cli compact ambiguousAcrossKinds, fusefs refFor — handled in later phases; no core test touches them.
